        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 65–69. Habitat of Didrepanephorus Wood-Mason, 1878 species. 65–67, habitat D. mucronatus Arrow, 1921: 65, forest in Mount Jinuoshan, Jinghong (Yunnan, China); 66–67, male attracted by light trap and stayed on a nearby bush in Dadu- gang (Yunnan, China); 68, male of D. nishiyamai Muramoto, 2006 on the ground (Guangxi, China; photograph by Chao Li); 69, male of D. subvittatus Benderitter, 1922 attracted by light trap and stayed on a nearby leaf in Mount Shiwandashan (Guangxi, China; photograph by Tao Zhang)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4556642/files/figure.png" .

